What do you have planned for me?

28:43.440 --> 28:45.600
Any job you need done,
I'm your man.

28:47.080 --> 28:48.080
Glad to hear it.

28:49.040 --> 28:51.000
They key is adding
to your resume,

28:51.160 --> 28:52.920
so you can start over.

28:55.560 --> 28:57.160
You can always start over.

28:57.680 --> 28:58.680
Right?

29:06.880 --> 29:08.080
Yes?

29:13.160 --> 29:15.720
Okay. I'm on my way.

29:18.160 --> 29:20.040
-You okay?
-It was my kid's school.

29:20.200 --> 29:21.480
I'll be right back.

29:28.840 --> 29:30.480
-Hello.
-Hi. Thanks for coming.

29:30.600 --> 29:33.000
